        "description": "\n## Welcome to MindEase API ðŸŒ¸\n\nMindEase is an AI-powered mood journal that uses GROQ AI \nto provide empathetic responses to your emotional entries.\n\n### Features\n- ðŸ¤– AI-powered emotional support responses\n- ðŸ“” Mood journal with history tracking  \n- ðŸ˜” Emoji-based mood selection\n- ðŸ’œ Powered by GROQ llama-3.1-8b-instant\n    ",
